Items can be moved async'ly through a web service to reach turned-off devices, or devices that can't connect to a local network (WP7).

Make Mover a file management app by allowing multiple folders (in the form of multiple tables) and a "throw it in", auto-org'd, searchable Archive.
Synchronize your Mover table with WebDAV to your Box.net, Dropbox, iDisk account to have everything on your PC/Mac without thinking.
